<Content>"HAPPY ENDING" I recently spent six wonderful nights at the Atlantic Beach Hotel in San Juan. Within one hour of my returning home I received a call from the general manager of the Atlantic Beach Hotel informing me that I had forgotten my jewelry bag with several pieces of my most prized and sentimental pieces of jewelry in the room. I was completely shocked as I had yet to unpack my luggage. The general manager assured me that all would be taken care of and not to worryThe following morning I was awaken at 8:30am to discover that my jewelry bag was being special delivered by a FedEx representative with all its contents intact, courtesy of the Atlantic Beach Hotel management. This to me was such a shock that they would go beyond the call of dutie to make sure I had safely received my valuables.I feel I was so blessed to regain my jewelry, not only for the monetary value, but for its sentimental value. My sincere thanks and gratitude go out to the entire staff and management and especially the honest and wonderful housekeepers. It makes me so proud that we still have such honest, conscience and caring people in this world that we live in.Thank You so much Atlantic Beach Hotel. 
